OL,3,CStruggling to sleep? Why muggy nights
OL,4,Care set to return this week
OL,6,FHas anyone else been struggling to
OL,7,Fsleep over the past few nights?
OL,9,FWhile it might not be as hot as May's
OL,10,Frecord-breaking temperatures, a very
OL,11,Fdifferent type of heat is sweeping
OL,12,Facross the UK - and it's set to be
OL,13,Fpretty uncomfortable.
OL,15,FBy the end of the week, increasingly
OL,16,Fstuffy and muggy air is forecast to
OL,17,Fseep into much of the UK - so here is
OL,18,Fwhy you might be struggling to get
OL,19,Fyour forty winks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
