OL,3,CStruggling to sleep? Why muggy nights
OL,4,Care set to return this week
OL,6,FWhy will it feel so different in the
OL,7,Fnext few days?
OL,9,FMuch of Europe is heating up this
OL,10,Fweek, with temperatures soaring above
OL,11,F30C and beyond 35C.
OL,13,FOur proximity to Europe means we are
OL,14,Flikely to receive some of this heat,
OL,15,Fwith temperatures set to climb across
OL,16,Fthe south-east and eastern areas.
OL,17,FHowever, this will be a gradual
OL,18,Fprocess.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
