OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781635704
OL,3,CStruggling to sleep? Why muggy nights
OL,4,Care set to return this week
OL,6,FTemperatures look likely to reach 25
OL,7,Fto 28C in many places, with some areas
OL,8,Fpeaking at up to 30C.
OL,10,FFurther north and west, temperatures
OL,11,Fwill be a little cooler, with a
OL,12,Ffresher feel.
OL,14,FAlthough these temperatures will not
OL,15,Fbe as exceptional, this episode of
OL,16,Fwarmth will bring increasingly muggy
OL,17,Fand humid air during both day and
OL,18,Fnight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
