OL,3,CStruggling to sleep? Why muggy nights
OL,4,Care set to return this week
OL,6,FIt will feel like a stark contrast to
OL,7,Fthe cool, fresh, and sometimes
OL,8,Fblustery, rainy conditions of June so
OL,9,Ffar.
OL,11,FWhere will we see the muggy and humid
OL,12,Fair?
OL,14,FThe humid conditions will be most
OL,15,Fnotable across the south-east and
OL,16,Fsouthern areas, especially inland.
OL,17,FCoastal stretches will have the chance
OL,18,Fof a freshening breeze.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
