PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781635704
OL,3,CStruggling to sleep? Why muggy nights
OL,4,Care set to return this week
OL,6,FEven though we often see higher
OL,7,Ftemperatures in the summer months, the
OL,8,Fhumidity will mean a warmer and more
OL,9,Funcomfortable feel, especially in
OL,10,Furban areas.
OL,12,FThere's also a high chance of some
OL,13,Fstuffy, restless nights.
OL,15,FOvernight on Friday night, it's
OL,16,Funlikely to be below 17/18C - that is
OL,17,Fhigher than some daytime temperatures
OL,18,Frecorded this month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
