PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781635704
OL,3,CStruggling to sleep? Why muggy nights
OL,4,Care set to return this week
OL,6,FIt will be slightly warmer in much of
OL,7,Fthe northern and western UK than in
OL,8,Frecent days.
OL,10,FMuggy air will gradually increase here
OL,11,Fby the end of the week, but it'll feel
OL,12,Fmuch more manageable and comfortable.
OL,14,FHow long will the warm and humid air
OL,15,Flast?
OL,17,FAt this stage, temperatures are likely
OL,18,Fto peak near 30C on Friday, but the
OL,19,Fvery warm and muggy air will remain
OL,20,Fthrough the weekend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
