PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781635704
OL,3,CStruggling to sleep? Why muggy nights
OL,4,Care set to return this week
OL,6,FWith the rise in humidity comes an
OL,7,Fincreased risk of thunderstorms.
OL,9,FThese will initially develop across
OL,10,Fthe continent and extend from France
OL,11,Finto the southern areas of the UK from
OL,12,FThursday evening.
OL,14,FThere are signs of keeping the
OL,15,Fmuggier, thundery air into the weekend.
OL,17,FIt will stay very warm, but
OL,18,Ftemperatures will be prevented from
OL,19,Frising higher as more clouds are
OL,20,Fexpected as thunderstorms develop.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
